# **App Name**: Sentinel — Intelligent Night Safety Companion

## Core Features:

- Live Sentinel Tracking: Real-time GPS tracking with cinematic dark-mode route visualization and shared live locations with trusted contacts.
- AI Anomaly Detection: An AI tool that monitors device sensors like the accelerometer and gyroscope to detect sudden sprinting or impacts, deciding when to trigger emergency check-ins.
- Safe Route Intelligence: An AI tool that suggests safer paths by evaluating environmental factors like lighting and movement density to decide the lowest-risk route.
- One-Tap Emergency SOS: Multi-method distress activation (button, shake, or voice) that broadcasts GPS coordinates and starts emergency recordings with Firestore synchronization.
- Circle of Trust: A contact management system for priority responders and relationship tagging, stored securely in Cloud Firestore.
- De-escalation Call Simulator: A highly realistic, customizable fake incoming call interface designed to help users safely exit uncomfortable social situations.
- Safety Voice Companion: An AI-driven verbal support system providing check-ins and safety awareness prompts using advanced text-to-speech technology.
- Quick Escape Stealth Mode: A UI feature that instantly masks the application with a decoy interface like a calculator or notes for discreet protection.
- Smart Trust Score System: An AI tool that generates a live safety confidence score by reasoning over movement behavior, location activity, and battery status.
- Nearby Safe Places: Integration with Google Places API to identify and navigate to police stations, hospitals, and open 24/7 public spaces.

## Style Guidelines:

- Primary Background: Obsidian Emerald (#040D08) for a deep, cinematic, and professional night-mode experience.
- Primary Accent: Royal Emerald (#10B981) to convey safety, vitality, and advanced technological precision.
- Secondary Surfaces: Deep Forest Gray (#0F1713) for elevated glassmorphic cards and subtle UI depth.
- Emergency Accents: High-Stakes Crimson (#E11D48) and Warning Amber (#F59E0B) for immediate visual identification of safety alerts.
- Headlines use 'Poppins' for a clean, premium look; body text uses 'Inter' for high-contrast legibility in low-light environments.
- Floating glassmorphic architecture with 28px corner rounding and ultra-thin emerald-tinted borders for a sophisticated aesthetic.
- Precision-engineered line icons with subtle emerald outer-glow effects to maintain clarity and a futuristic HUD feel.
- Elegant, organic motion transitions and a soft breathing pulse effect for active tracking indicators.